missioning, and operation phase 2X350 MW M/s Thermal power plant project at Nellore, A.P.; ➢ An appreciation certificate received from M/s NALCO management for 6M LTI free safe manhours.; ➢ Two times appreciation certificate received from M/s NALCO management forBest safety system implementation during"}]'::jsonb, 'F:\Resume All 1\Resume PDF\Suryakanta Patra 25122023_231225_175937.pdf', 'Name: Applicant- Suryakanta Patra

